    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Category 9: Operational Resilience\nUptime, disaster recovery, and operational resilience capabilities.\n\n**Governance topics**: Cyber, EA, TPRM",
      "id": "Field_Cat9_Header"
    },
    {
      "type": "separator",
      "id": "Field_Cat9_Sep1"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_1",
      "label": "C9.1: Uptime SLA and historical uptime (past 12 months)",
      "type": "textfield",
      "key": "c9_1"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_2",
      "label": "C9.2: Redundancy and failover architecture",
      "type": "textarea",
      "key": "c9_2"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_3",
      "label": "C9.3: Geographic redundancy (multi-region/multi-AZ)",
      "type": "textarea",
      "key": "c9_3"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_4",
      "label": "C9.4: Disaster recovery RTO/RPO by service tier",
      "type": "textarea",
      "key": "c9_4"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_5",
      "label": "C9.5: Last DR test date and results summary",
      "type": "textarea",
      "key": "c9_5"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_6",
      "label": "C9.6: Incident management process (ITIL or equivalent)",
      "type": "textarea",
      "key": "c9_6"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_7",
      "label": "C9.7: Status page and real-time monitoring availability",
      "type": "textarea",
      "key": "c9_7"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_8",
      "label": "C9.8: Capacity planning and auto-scaling capabilities",
      "type": "textarea",
      "key": "c9_8"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_9",
      "label": "C9.9: Dependency mapping (critical upstream/downstream services)",
      "type": "textarea",
      "key": "c9_9"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_10",
      "label": "C9.10: Planned maintenance windows and notification process",
      "type": "textarea",
      "key": "c9_10"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_11",
      "label": "C9.11: DORA compliance (if EU-regulated)",
      "type": "textarea",
      "key": "c9_11"
    },
    {
      "id": "Field_C9_12",
      "label": "C9.12: Maximum tolerable downtime per month",
      "type": "textfield",
      "key": "c9_12"
